{"tid":1544531,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先有份食加藤屋既入哂黎","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T10:42:54.000Z","uid":51234,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3a0deedf47cfac6e12ccbc0c651bcdc79762f7","tid":1544531,"uid":51234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"人地都估唔到短時間內有咁多人黎幫襯，多人到啲職員都話4個要分開坐，樓面又得果兩個人，又要落單又要上餐又要收野執檯又要收錢又要派飛安排位，拎飛果陣人地都好心講左句&rdquo;好多人呀等到就等啦&rdquo;，唔等得既唔明點解重要係度燥等diu鳩個店員，大家都係去支持姐，無耐性既真係多你一個唔多，排支那啲野飲野食又唔見你咁？淨係依啲小事都露哂啲国人醜惡底，重點長底抗爭呀，我diu哂你地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">似返哂個香港人<br />\n比啲人情味互相體諒下啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"d2c5eac6e34aa8f122556227e3b6ae05a4f46d45","tid":1544531,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92884f8c33850653d86794817a29377da43f34ed","tid":1544531,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n好撚好聽<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=d5bd3a3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJuEF0r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJuEF0r.gif&h=a8c24eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74456e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"4f6224e2208ceb0905b27ea9c8ddcad93d980ef1","tid":1544531,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d28213e2cdda1f298703f1fc564a4545ff1fc9a","tid":1544531,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:58:16.000Z","msg":"其實真係做死D員工"},{"pid":"be9192f31f3e500c54d3fabafc80625ae3e7d3e2","tid":1544531,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":